quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  55,26,Everyone on it is perishing
  55,27,"but forever will remain the Face of your Lord, full of Majesty and Glory"
  55,28,So which of your Lord's blessings will you deny
  55,29,To Him turn everyone in the heavens and on earth for their needs; and every day He manifests Himself in yet another way
  55,30,So which of your Lord's blessings will you deny
  55,31,"We will soon attend to your judgment, you burdensome two"
  55,32,So which of your Lord's blessings will you deny
  55,33,"Jinn and Humankind, if you are able to break through the confines of the heavens and earth, then break through them. You will not break through except with authority"
  55,34,So which of your Lord's blessings will you deny
  55,35,"A flash of fire and brass will be sent against you, and you will not be helped"
  55,36,So which of your Lord's blessings will you deny
  55,37,And when the heaven is split open and becomes rose-colored like oil
  55,38,So which of your Lord's blessings will you deny
  55,39,"On that Day, no human and no jinn will be asked about his sins"
  55,40,So which of your Lord's blessings will you deny
  55,41,"Those who forced others to reject Our messages, will be known by their marks, and they will be seized by the foreheads and the feet"
  55,42,So which of your Lord's blessings will you deny
  55,43,"This is Hell, which those who forced others to reject Our messages denied"
  55,44,They will circulate them between fire and scalding water
  55,45,So which of your Lord's blessings will you deny